KANO – Unknown gunmen at the early hours of Wednesday abducted Hajiya Zainab, mother of Isiyaku Ali Danja, former Speaker, Kano House of Assembly. Briefing newsmen over the development, Ali Danja said the abductors are yet to establish contact with the family. Though Kano Police Command is yet to comment on the development, security sources have it that the heavily armed assailants forced their way into Hajiya Zainab’s residence at Gezawa around 1:00 a.m, seized and took her away to an unknown destination. Gunmen Kill Seven Family Members, 17 Others In Fresh Kaduna… Gunmen Kill District Head, Four Others And Abduct Many In… Details soon